ly-issue-153/#disqus_thread">0 条评论</a></span>							<span class="tag-list"><i class="material-icons">&#xE2C8;</i><a href="/tag/androiddevweekly/">AndroidDevWeekly</a></span>						</div>					</div>					<div class="content">						<div class="post-entry">							<h3 id="">新闻</h3><ol><li><a href="http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/soft/665633.htm">Android 8.1 可能会让用户 Chromebook 发送和接收短信</a></li></ol><h3 id="">教程</h3><ol><li><p><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/1YRhXOs61u8_fRU1wMaFyA">有货 App HTTPS 优化探索和实践</a></p></li><li><p><a href="http://drakeet.me/android-studio-and-gradle-3-0-guide/">Android Studio 和 Gradle 3.0.0 更新简明指南</a></p></li><li><p><a href="http://www.jianshu.com/p/e574f0ffdb42">不可思议的OOM</a></p></li><li><p><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/30559224">Android系统中动画浅析</a></p></li></ol><h3 id="app">开源库 &amp; App</h3><ol><li><p><a href="https://github.com/HelmMobile/KotlinCleanArchitecture">KotlinCleanArchitecture</a></p><p>Approach to Clean Architecture in Kotlin</p></li><li><p><a href="https://github.com/NoNews/NoPermission">NoPermission</a></p><p>Simple Android library for permissions request. Consists of only one class.</p></li><li><p><a href="https://github.com/battleent/android-RibbonViews">android-RibbonViews</a></p><p>This is an android view library "RibbonViews"</p></li><li><p><a href="https://github.com/whalemare/RxValidator2">RxValidator2</a></p><p>The simplest way to add reactive validation to your app</p></li><li><p><a href="https://github.com/wenqin-231/StatusView">StatusView</a></p><p>帮助用户轻松简单的创建 Loading、Error、Empty、DialogLoading 等自定义布局的库</p></li><li><p><a href="https://github.com/Tencent/RapidView">RapidView</a></p><p>一套用于开发 Android 客户端界面、逻辑以及功能的开发组件。布局文件(XML)及逻辑文件(Lua)可以运行时执行，主要用以解决 Android 客户端界面、逻辑快速更新以及快速开发的诉求。</p></li><li><p><a href="https://github.com/wangchenyan/LrcView">LrvView</a></p><p>一款优雅的可拖动歌词控件</p></li><li><p><a href="https://github.com/lsjwzh/FastTextView">FastTextView</a></p><p>去除了 Android TextView 中多余的处理环节，大幅优化 measure 时的速度</p></li></o